{"tid":1004256,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[點搞呀]巴士「刺客」被控6罪 轉介區域法院情人節再訊","createTime":"2019-02-01T09:59:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-03T05:32:43.000Z","uid":7439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cb47e17ba524b4ab4e3acd341cf7bf4804e2eca5","tid":1004256,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T09:59:29.000Z","msg":"去年九巴接連有座位遭人插針或放針，有乘客遭刺臀及刺大腿，其後一名涉及至少3案的無業「刺客」被捕，他疑因不滿九巴「飛站」而作案，案件在沙田法院再訊。經控方修訂和新增控罪後，被告莫湛深現被控企圖有意圖而傷人和刑事損壞共6罪，繼續毋須答辯。裁判官將案押後到2月14日轉介區院再訊，期間被告繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指被告莫湛深於去年6月27日，在兩輛巴士的座位共三度放針，意圖使坐在上面的人受傷。他另被控在同一日，在該兩輛巴士三度刑事損壞上層座位。"},{"pid":"7a6154c6f5c2e33e919c2ec8473a8529988840d5","tid":1004256,"uid":33605,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:00:11.000Z","msg":"N Ben<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24c3a7cec031dc38c29fcf2dc966367b38980707","tid":1004256,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:00:59.000Z","msg":"裁判官Magistrate :<br />\n王詩麗署理主任裁判官 Ms. WONG Sze-lai, Acting Principal Magistrate <br />\n<br />\nSTCC2565/2018<br />\n莫湛深 MOK, CHAM-SUM<br />\n<br />\n(1)傷人<br />\n(1)Wounding<br />\n(2)傷人<br />\n(2)Wounding<br />\n(3)傷人<br />\n(3)Wounding<br />\n(4)企圖傷人<br />\n(4)Attempted Wounding<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家仲多埋刑事損壞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65ee47c5346a4b7f8d29abb35075c1df245a0e9","tid":1004256,"uid":886,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:03:21.000Z","msg":"橫掂N ben情人節無野做，無所謂啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"169137e4d0f4cea37105893a0f6d365ba20fe104","tid":1004256,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T10:08:04.000Z","msg":"港毒之父來"},{"pid":"7ef343121289f826e2a3fed3e39929070f728e31","tid":1004256,"uid